  "text": "\"There is considerable and unhelpful confusion in the way the term 'continuous improvement' is used, since it is deployed both as a verbthe process whereby a continuous stream of innovations emerge -and also as a noun, referring to the outcome of that process\" [CITATION_1] ).",
